  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Companion Appearance Enhancement</span>. Ideal for fierce-tempered companions, this stylish plate armour protects vital organs against laser and projectile fire. Ultra-soft breathable padding reduces the likelihood of companions wriggling out of the accessory.<br><br>Earn the trust of wild animals to adopt companions. Interact with companions to customise their appearance.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "专属的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">同伴外观强化</span>。这套风格别致的板甲最适合习性凶猛的同伴，能够有效帮助重要器官抵挡激光与投射物攻击。极其柔软的可呼吸垫能够降低同伴挣脱装饰品的可能性。<br><br>获取野生动物的信任以将其收养为同伴。与同伴互动来为其调整外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特<span class=\"name name-stellar\">同伴外觀強化</span>。這款時髦的板甲非常適合脾氣暴躁的同伴，可以保護重要器官免受雷射和射彈的傷害。超柔軟透氣襯墊可減少配件從同伴身上滑脫的可能性。<br><br>獲得野生動物的信任，即可收養為同伴。與同伴互動，自訂其外觀。"
  },
